      "span_text": "We evaluate our model on three datasets: SPMRL (Modern Standard Arabic), classical Arabic and CTB5 (Chinese). Our model consistently outperforms state-of-the-art systems designed for these languages. We obtain a 2.1% TedEval gain against the best published results in the 2013 SPMRL shared task [CITATION_1] ."
